{"tid":1041667,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"光爆全場！訓練員睇戲都照玩　4機齊上勁騷擾","createTime":"2019-03-01T04:25:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-01T05:02:05.000Z","uid":225464,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"79dc5f7a171e1be4b34eaa575ae9e94a0737a1b8","tid":1041667,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T04:25:24.000Z","msg":"<strong>光爆全場！訓練員睇戲都照玩 4機齊上勁騷擾</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2tHjbUr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2tHjbUr&d=oVHkeUedSvD9nF4ig%2BuBMNAsgxU2M8QNPxyQAqp636I%3D&h=f0d3f864\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2tHjbUr</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190301/photo/bkn-20190301113722224-0301_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190301121745\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190301%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190301113722224-0301_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190301121745&h=59f91eff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日夜鍛練去取勝？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「唔該熄埋個Pad Pad好嗎？光到我就嚟睇唔到嘢㗎啦」。近日有人觀賞電影時，遇上兩名「訓練員」一邊看戲，一邊開着電話及平板電腦大玩Pok&eacute;mon Go，怒斥他們極為騷擾。<br />\n<br />\n據Facebook群組「柴灣人柴灣事」周三（27日）的貼文表示，事主在柴灣一間戲院看電影時，忽然發現前排的座位突然「一片光明」。他好奇之下察看，發現原來有人開着遊戲「捉精靈」。4個屏幕同時發出的光度，令他大感騷擾。<br />\n<br />\n事主批評：「點解要入戲院捉，騷擾其他人睇戲，入戲院唔係睇戲咩？」離場後，他又發現兩人繼續邊行邊捉，嘆謂︰「真係捉少一陣都唔可以」？<br />\n<br />\n有網友留言怒斥：「不知所謂」、「自私到一個點」，有人又建議事主：「開手機燈幫佢照明」、「對付呢啲人要出聲先得」。"},{"pid":"62c02b032ae821a6b8135972bbd1914ce3dd9132","tid":1041667,"uid":106426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T04:26:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"00074a7999d6db07621cdbecc06708772fa44e3d","tid":1041667,"uid":40569,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T04:26:59.000Z","msg":"戲院入面收到data架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40848ed90d99f60fc7b90e6b37b922c85c333f6f","tid":1041667,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T04:28:53.000Z","msg":"屌鳩佢都唔撚識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即場開佢波啦,依啲賤種我見一隻屌一隻"},{"pid":"891bb02ce07cc1104f8ccd32ce08e46e1d7443f4","tid":1041667,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T04:31:18.000Z","msg":"廢中廢老？"},{"pid":"84c126afb95a6e0b74803003cc0452e046bac7ca","tid":1041667,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T05:02:05.000Z","msg":"即場屌啦"}]}